  "text": "Hierarchical clustering was done using the CLUSTER 3.0 program (http://bonsai.ims.u-tokyo ac.jp/ mdehoon/software/cluster/) [CITATION_1] , and clusters were viewed by the JAVA TREEVIEW program (http://jtreeview.sourceforge.net/) [CITATION_2] . EXCEL was used for all data analysis.",
